#X text 564 65 Here we have basically the same example. But now we have a stereo patch based on [superosc~] (a wave stacking oscillator \, where we stack 5 of them)! The stereo is taken care via multichannel connections. As a variation \, we also have the [moog~] filter instead and note that it has a buil-in overdrive feature. For last \, we're retriggering the LFO at every new note., f 48;
